    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a breathtaking 2011 BMW M3 Competition Package, a masterclass in naturally aspirated engineering. This S65 V8 powerhouse has been fastidiously maintained with an open-wallet approach; proactive rod bearing replacement was completed using VAC-coated shells and ARP hardware to ensure bottom-end longevity. The M-DCT dual-clutch transmission features the GTS software flash for lightning-fast shift maps, while the Electronic Damper Control (EDC) provides surgical precision through the corners. The paint depth is consistent across all panels, showing no signs of orange peel or clear coat failure, and the interior Novillo leather remains supple with zero bolster wear. Recent service includes new throttle actuators and a fresh fill of Liqui Moly 10W-60. This is a turn-key, zero-compromise machine for the buyer who understands the nuance of a perfectly calibrated chassis.",
      "price": 48900.0,
