    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Imagine the golden hour, the sun dipping below the horizon as you glide through winding coastal roads in this automotive masterpiece. This isn't just a car; it\u2019s a time capsule of elegance and raw emotion. Every curve of its silhouette tells a story of precision engineering and timeless design. The cabin welcomes you with the scent of heritage, offering a sanctuary where the world outside fades into a blur of speed and style. To drive this is to command a legend, a rare opportunity to own a piece of history that remains as breathtaking today as the moment it first took flight.",
